{
  "stem": "5810.4",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so if you had to be called at any time, and in that-- and that was just about the Korean War, the Korean conflict was still going on.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And certain things in Israel were happening in Lebanon and so on we're going on.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they were very much afraid to start you off on a career and lose you.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I said, well, if I can't start-- I, I just can't go on being a shipping boy in a, in a grocery store.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Why don't I then join the American army and go into-- take on this much schooling as I can and get rid of it, and then be able to apply for at least a career?",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Which I did, but in those days, you had to join for three years if you enlisted.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then came a couple of other things that, that tore my life apart.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was the end of the Korean conflict, as I said.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was just beginning to end.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And at that time, there was a good chance of my winding up in Korea right after the basic training, which, because of some background that they understood, they decided, with the story that I was giving them, that maybe this would not be a good idea.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it's unusual to have the American Army understanding that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But then came another, another thing that, that happened, that was the most amazing thing.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I went to a school that I had a chance to go to, field radio repair.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And upon graduation, you were always sent someplace else to put your skills at use.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I got my orders to go to Germany.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I must tell you, in 1956, the wounds were still very much open.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
